  <releases>
    <release version="1.0.7" date="2022-01-22" urgency="medium">
      <description>
        <p>Consistent support for dark/ light mode and accent color on timeseries chart view</p>
        <p>Added sub navigation on timeseries chart view for toggling legend and filtering related metric tags</p>
        <p>The journal view now opens immediately on application start if there are log entries</p>
        <p>Updated elementary OS Sdk to runtime version 6.1</p>
        <p>Replaced LiveChart.StaticChart with WebKit.WebView</p>
      </description>
    </release>
